extends /sites/VirtualCricketLeague/layouts/base.pug

block variables
    - const title = 'Privacy Policy | VirtualCricketLeague – Your Data, Your Control'
    - const description = 'Learn how VirtualCricketLeague collects, uses, and protects your data. Read our Privacy Policy to understand your rights and how we ensure your information stays secure.'

block content
    +Header()

    main
        section.container.privacy-policy
            h1 Privacy Policy for VirtualCricketLeague
            p At VirtualCricketLeague, we value the privacy of our users. On our website, virtualcricketleague.com, we are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and the measures we take to keep it secure.
            p If you have any questions regarding our Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us.

            h2 Log Data
            p Like many websites, VirtualCricketLeague collects log data to track visits and interactions. This data includes your IP address, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), date and time of visit, pages viewed, and the number of clicks. This information is anonymized and used for website analysis, security monitoring, and improving user experience.

            h2 Third-Party Services
            p We may use third-party services for analytics, website optimization, and advertisements. These services help us understand user interactions and improve the platform, but they do not collect personally identifiable information.

            h2 Advertising Partners
            p Our website works with third-party advertisers who may collect data to provide relevant ads. Each advertising partner has its own Privacy Policy, which we recommend reviewing for details on their data collection and use.

            h2 Privacy Policies of Advertising Partners
            p While we provide information about VirtualCricketLeague’s advertising partners, we do not control their privacy practices. Please refer to their respective Privacy Policies for details on how they manage user data.

            h2 Children's Privacy
            p We prioritize protecting children’s privacy online. We encourage parents and guardians to be involved in their children’s internet activities.

            p VirtualCricketLeague does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under the age of 18. If you believe your child has shared such information on our website, please contact us immediately so we can take action to remove it.

            h2 Online Privacy Policy Scope
            p This Privacy Policy applies only to online interactions on virtualcricketleague.com and governs how we handle user data shared on our platform. It does not cover data collected offline or through external channels.

            h2 Consent
            p By using our website, you acknowledge and agree to our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.

            p If you have any further questions about our Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us.


    +Footer()